">  </span><span class=\"n\">fin_cases</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;;&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rfl</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
